Version 0.02 - Sunday 1st April 2007
    + Changed to OO interface.

    + Added chroot functionality on master parent process.
      
    + Added aliases for various methods.

    + Changed storage of initial cwd and script filename to
      constants in a begin block to make safe from
      modifications.

    + Disallowed daemonisation of the master process more
      than once.


Version 0.01 - Sunday 11th February 2007
    + Nothing much changed.


Version 0.00_1 - Monday 29th May 2006
    + Pre-release.

